    <title>Configure programs in the Programs/Attributes app (legacy app)</title>
    <para>
        <note>
            <title>Changes in how you configure programs from version 2.27</title>
            <itemizedlist>
                <listitem>
                    <para>You create program indicators and program rules in the <emphasis
                            role="bold">Maintenance</emphasis> app. It's no longer possible to
                        create program indicators and program rules in the legacy <emphasis
                            role="bold">Program / Attributes</emphasis> app.</para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                    <para>You can create event programs (programs without registration) in the
                            <emphasis role="bold">Maintenance</emphasis> app. The old version of
                        this functionality is also available in the legacy <emphasis role="bold"
                            >Program / Attributes</emphasis> app.</para>
                </listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
        </note>
    </para>
